<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Your OTP Code</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { background-color: #f8f8f8; font-family: 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #333; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 560px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08); }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #b91c1c); padding: 36px 40px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; }
    .header p  { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 6px; }
    .body { padding: 40px; text-align: center; }
    .body p { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: #555; text-align: left; }
    .otp-box { margin: 32px auto; display: inline-block; background: #fef2f2; border: 2px dashed #dc2626; border-radius: 12px; padding: 20px 48px; }
    .otp-code { font-size: 42px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 12px; color: #dc2626; font-family: 'Courier New', monospace; }
    .expiry { margin-top: 8px; font-size: 13px; color: #888; }
    .warning { margin-top: 24px; padding: 14px 16px; background: #fff7ed; border-left: 3px solid #f97316; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; text-align: left; }
    .warning p { font-size: 13px; color: #c2410c; }
    .footer { background: #f4f4f4; padding: 24px 40px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #eee; }
    .footer p { font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; line-height: 1.6; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>🔑 Verify your account</h1>
      <p>Use the OTP code below to complete verification</p>
    </div>

    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi <strong>{{name}}</strong>,</p>
      <br/>
      <p>Enter this OTP code to verify your account. Do not share this code with anyone.</p>

      <div class="otp-box">
        <div class="otp-code">{{otp}}</div>
        <div class="expiry">Expires in <strong>{{expiresInMinutes}} minutes</strong></div>
      </div>

      <div class="warning">
        <p>⚠️ If you did not request this code, please ignore this email or contact support immediately.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>© {{year}} Social Hub. All rights reserved.<br/>This is an automated email, please do not reply.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
